    <PackageId>I-Synergy.Framework.EventSourcing.Storage.Azure</PackageId>
    <Description>Azure Blob Storage implementation of IEventArchiveStorage for I-Synergy Event Sourcing</Description>
    <PackageTags>I-Synergy, Framework, EventSourcing, Azure, BlobStorage, Archive, CQRS</PackageTags>
